Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,《纸牌屋》前情提要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来就是为了让我空欢喜一场吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what, you just came over here to get my hopes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是为了确保你今晚不去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came here to make sure that you don't go to church tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟塔斯克叫劲又得不到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing to gain by locking horns with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不喜欢矛盾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not a man who likes conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是故意想毁掉总统吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you intentionally trying to destroy the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你有钱  雷蒙德  但我有权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may have all the money, Raymond, but I have all the men with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  这是故意的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, was this intentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天可能要关闭两座电厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may need to take two of my plants offline tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,作不定期维修\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for unscheduled maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-这绝对不行    -安全第一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, that's unacceptable.   - Safety comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不希望出事故\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了佐伊·巴恩斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you kill Zoe Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会像对待其他报道一样对待这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna treat this the way I would any other story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许不会喜欢我写的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might not like what I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我看起来像是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It makes me seem crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-你犯了罪    -但不包括谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You committed a crime.   - Not murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他要逃脱罪责了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna get away with it, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}缺乏经验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,泰瑞·乌麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terry Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}唯唯诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃·博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}不问时事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沃克总统面对着一个千疮百孔的国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Walker has surrounded himself with a broken Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至还提拔国会的人进白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He even brought one of them into the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们整垮了经济\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, they've broken the economy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还与中国起了争端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and put us on a collision course with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,趁来得及  快阻止他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put a stop to them before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}废物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在中期选举中表明立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send a message at the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让美国变得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's start fixing the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}为美国投票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,由美国进步之友赞助播出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Paid for by Friends of a Better America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,两千五百万  凭空变出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Twenty-five million? Out of thin air?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-初步估计是这样    -钱是哪来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's our estimate.   - Where is the money coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-超级政治行动委员会    -这广告是攻击具体事件的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Super PACs.   - These are issue-based attack ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,钱是谁给的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So who's giving to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,得等这季财报才能确定来源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't trace the money until this quarter's filings come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,中期选举栽了  下次大选也泡汤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We get killed in the midterms, we can kiss 2016 goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,共和党就会占据国会多数席位和白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can deal with the republican majority and a Republican president.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和民主党议会竞选委员会在努力还击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're trying to counter with D-trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,凭空变出两千五百万吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make 25 million appear out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少能造出点声势    -那不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can make a dent.   - Dents don't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不管款筹得多快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, no matter how fast we ramp up fundraising,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都补不上缺口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can't close the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,得切断他们的资金来源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to stop their money flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,找到源头  釜底抽薪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Locate the source and then cut off the tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,凭空出现这么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With this sorta influx you can be sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有人违规了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}somebody's not playing by the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但找不到源头就没法告状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we can't whistle-blow until we find the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去找  而且赶快找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then find it. And you sure as hell better find it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在构思还击的对策\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, I've been working on a proposal to counter the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,协调全国上下发出消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A coordinated national messaging effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明天晚些时候发给你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be sending all of you copies later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要考虑一切办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we should be open to every idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  去干活儿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, go. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你本该代表我控制国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were supposed to steer Congress on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我心情无比焦虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one is as concerned as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真应该把你留在国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shoulda kept you in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,向雷蒙德最初说的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like Raymond suggested from day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可你分心去掺和参议院  国情咨文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you've been distracted by the Senate, State of the Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还干预外交\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}meddling with foreign diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-是你要我去谈判的    -我知道我做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You asked me to negotiate--   - I know what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I know where it's gotten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  攻击我们的广告不是因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, the attack ads are not a result of anything--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你慌慌忙忙地到处扑火  而不是防止失火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're scrambling from fire to fire instead of preventing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是联邦选举委员会  不能变魔...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not the FEC, I can't wave a wand--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别就知道找借口  弗兰克  你不止这点本事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me more than excuses, Frank! You're better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没准就是这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是想找个沙袋撒气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you need a punching bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就站在这儿让你出气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will stand here and take the punches,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,自我上任以来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as I have done time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一次次做你的沙袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since I swore my oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可我更想照你的吩咐  回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would much rather get back to work, as you've asked me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你太过分了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are out of line, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不出拳就放我走吧  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dismiss me or keep swinging, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
