Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,丹·拉尼根转投那边了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dan Lanagin switched teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,共和党的大捐助人都没什么异常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't find any anomalies among big Republican donors,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我查了民主党的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I checked our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根这季一分都没捐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lanagin hasn't given a dime this quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  没捐和资助共和党不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but not giving isn't the same as giving to the Republicans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他赌场的账目  安永事务所做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His casino's accounts. Ernst and Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,捐了一千八百万  还不是给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eighteen million for donations, and they're not going to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么弄到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you get your hands on those?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我有朋友  所以你才找我帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got friends. That's why you solicit my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那广告花了大约两千五百万\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The estimate for the ad buys was 25 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,账目只到6月30日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those accounts are up to date as of June 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后应该还捐款了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They could have made more donations since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根的赌场在密苏里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lanagin's casino is in Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德·塔斯克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我和总统有不满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got an axe to grind with me and with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,选举委员会的文件里没他的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never seen his name on any FEC filings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他从不捐助政党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't make political contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才能进退自如\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how he remains flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他在想办法筹集资金吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think he's funneling the money somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你去堪萨斯城  去那家赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get yourself to Kansas City. I want you in that casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-是  先生    -我会继续查的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir.   - I'll keep digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接我太太的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-你从哪得到的菜谱    -我父亲教我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where'd you get the recipe?   - My father taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-你跟你爸爸很亲密吗    -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You and your dad were close?   - Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,烹饪肋排是那混蛋唯一能做好的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cooking ribs was the only thing that motherfucker did right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-这话不能上报纸吧    -我有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I guess you can't print that.   - I have ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的会上报纸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This really gonna be in the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,至少能上波士顿的报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least in Boston, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么觉得没人会在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't see why anybody would care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是关于个人喜好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's a personal interest story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么多餐厅  美国副总统却偏偏喜欢这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president of the United States comes here, of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是说这破地方吗    -我可没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You mean this shithole?   - That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是泰姬陵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the Taj Mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他从什么时候开始来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long has he been coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有20年了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About 20 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是个好人  弗兰克    -你还叫他弗兰克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's a good man, Frank.   - You still call him Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里  我才是总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, in this joint, I'm the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是副总统  也是国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the vice president and the Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是一名顾客  忠实的顾客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just another customer. A loyal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他才喜欢这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think that's why he likes it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你像对待普通人那样对待他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you treat him like a regular person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧  不过主要还是因为这肋排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe. Mostly it's the fuckin' ribs, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果失业率上升至20%以上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if unemployment goes up more than two-tenths,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望美联储考虑...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the Fed to consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}这个沙袋不像我话那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来点什么吗  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get you something, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我青柠苏打水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Club soda with lime, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-就这样吗    -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it?   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要吃的吗    -不用  就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nothing to eat?   - No. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是在戒酒  在这地方待着可挺受煎熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tough spot to hang out if you're in the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么知道    -酒鬼眼里分外明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How'd you know?   - Takes one to know one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-你多久了    -刚过一年  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How long?   - Little over a year. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就要15年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going on 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,赛马赢钱了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any luck with the ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  还没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,选个数字  1到12\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pick a number. One through twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,9\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,名声大噪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hot Fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,苏打水马上来  亲爱的  配青柠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Club soda coming up, darling. With lime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两小时他都没有动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hasn't moved the last two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也没跟任何人说话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he hasn't spoken to anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在赌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just been betting on the races.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要我们带他进来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want us to bring him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不  那是副总统的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. That's the vice president's chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别引发混乱  盯住他就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want to make a scene. Just keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他干了什么  去了哪里  跟谁说过话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me know what he does, where he goes, and who he talks to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  拉尼根先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got it, Mr. Lanagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你真该看看他们的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should've seen their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们彻底糊涂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They didn't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是我让他们扶住沙袋时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially when I made 'em hold the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你试过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tried it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sure as hell did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我那么冲你发脾气  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I lashed out at you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是我失礼了  有失妥当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I was disrespectful, and that was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的情绪最近总有些失控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My temper's gotten away from me these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时需要被人吼一吼  清醒过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to be jolted back into reality sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是出于好意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a -- a kind gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是消遣罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, just some good old fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎说我们这周要一起吃晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia tells me we're having dinner later this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  克莱尔也这样跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Claire tells me the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能离开这里几小时也不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it'll be good to get out of this place for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这幅画从肯尼迪时期就挂在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been here since Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是他出生那年画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was painted the same year he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,描绘的好像是一战的庆祝游行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It depicts, I think, a World War I parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,每一幅画我都该了解一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I should know every painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎懂不少呢  至少了解这幅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you seem to know quite a lot, at least about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想趁现在有机会  好好研究一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I try to soak it all in while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,痴迷于历史的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Presidents who obsess over history
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,痴迷于他们在历史中的地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}obsess about their place in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是如何创造历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}instead of forging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我  就在刚才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did. Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫  一整天都熙熙攘攘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, the White House. All day long it's buzzing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候却又如此冷清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and at this hour it's so desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做总统是件伟大而珍贵的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The presidency is a great and precious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而代价就是孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loneliness is the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做个假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's assume
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果杜鲁门总统就是坐在这其中一张椅子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in one of these chairs, staring at this wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着墙  决定投放核弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is where Truman decided to drop the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们会不会有什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And see if we feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没感觉  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  这儿很乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, it's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不用为我收拾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to clean up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你看到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn’t want you seeing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚穿着这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wore 'em last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个  还是我现在这身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You like these or you want the ones I'm wearing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在赌场工作多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long you been working in the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定见多识广\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bet you've seen a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我什么都见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah. I've seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了  要开早会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should get going. Got an early meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我留下来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想在这儿过夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't planning on sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一次一夜情吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, uh, another one-night stand then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的风格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧  你肯定是老手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. You must play the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但你很会调情啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you are such a flirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确会调情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I flirt, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只跟喜欢的人上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I only sleep with someone if I'm into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我喜欢留下过夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I prefer to stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米·丹顿  专情男子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy Danton, serial monogamist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在开玩笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不是...抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I didn't, uh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不是认真的  就不会有下一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This doesn't happen again unless it's leading somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我对自己想要的东西都很直接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm upfront about what I want, in all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是在政治上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not just politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,每年三四次  会有十几个有钱的中国人来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three or four times a year they fly in about a dozen Chinese guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,专门来烧钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Money to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把赌场一整层预留给他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They got a whole floor of the casino reserved just for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,据说能输掉几百万\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Word is they throw away millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明不了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that doesn't necessarily mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,中国人都爱赌博  特别是富人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Chinese love to gamble. Especially the rich ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  他们会去维加斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, in Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是密苏里  远多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Missouri. It's a much longer flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to find out --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人是从哪飞过来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where these planes are coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认识联邦航空管理局的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who do we know in the FAA?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识  但道尔认识  我让他去打探了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know anyone. But Doyle does. I already got him on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息就通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll text you when I hear back from Doyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  谢谢让我度过美好的一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Thanks for last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很开心    -不  才没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I had fun.   - No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想着别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were thinking of somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我十年戒酒纪念章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got that one after ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能给你带来好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope it brings you some luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法案由艾琳·布鲁克斯发起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elaine Brooks will be sponsoring
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,第一夫人已经认同了初稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the First Lady has approved the early draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬  看看那板子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie, take a look at the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你  想想还有谁能做联署人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get a sense of who might cosponsor, besides yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我们肯定能拉来不少重量级人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely. I'm sure we can lock down a lot of heavyweights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,洛莉和我会处理这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lorrie and I will get right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该想想媒体计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should talk about a media plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在还太早了    -难道不该宣传吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's premature for that.   - Don't we want to get this out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,尽早开始博取支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}start building support as soon as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-做活动和采访    -我只想看到最佳成效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Events, interviews?   - I want what's most effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体大肆宣扬不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A media blitz is the wrong way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,应该始终只用一个引子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want a single long lead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,与法案出台同步  要有档次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that coincides with the introduction of the bill. Something classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-但要广泛支持才能...    -大肆宣传\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But you want broad support, to hit--   - A blanket strategy will
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,能博取支持  但也可能招致批评\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}galvanize as many detractors as supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们把理念包装得当...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not if the message is framed in such way--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得先获取目标群体的认同  然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want a key demographic to get on board, and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-请让我说完    -然后慢慢积累\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let me finish, please.   - Then we let it percolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议找《纽约时代杂志》的马特·贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suggest Matt Bai, The New York Times Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这想法  非常喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like that idea. I like it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  你能和马特联系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So do I. Can you speak to Matt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先别定下来  接触一下看看情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No promises. Just test the waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意去找他谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm happy to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我和马特关系不错  我给他打个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got a good relationship with Matt. I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  赛斯  有进展随时通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. Seth, you keep me posted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这周晚些时候再碰个头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and let's all get together later this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你读一下法案  给我写份摘要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to read the bill and write me a summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈过之前  绝不要跟任何人透露一个字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not under any circumstances share it with anyone until we've spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不先过一遍议员名单吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't want to go over the board first, at least --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,关于堕胎查到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything on the abortion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一无所获  全都核实了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. It all checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-完全确定吗    -我方方面面都查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- One hundred percent?   - I turned over every stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-安德伍德夫人说的是实话    -我需要猛料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mrs. Underwood was telling the truth.   - We need something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,时间拖得太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫妇都很小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Underwoods are careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有丑闻  肯定藏得非常深\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they have skeletons, they're buried deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是"如果"的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a question of "If."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克这样的人肯定有丑闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody like Frank is gonna have skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那我会挖出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你这边一无所获  我就没法向上面交代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't deliver, that means I don't deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的风格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I always deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了我这个任务  而且期望我做好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave me an assignment with high expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望的  但也别指望一蹴而就\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will meet them. But it's not gonna happen overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以别跟我颐指气使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So don't fuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是你雇来办事的人  不是你的走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a hired gun. Not one that you own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你能达成目的就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As long as you hit the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那你得帮我个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳·埃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor Ellis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没他碍事的话我会拥有更多权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have more access if he isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能找个美差把他引走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrange a cushy job offer for him somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,私企还是政府部门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Private or public sector?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,私企的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,收入丰厚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让他难以拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something he can't turn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给  先付一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, this is half.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等我完成任务时再付我钱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can pay me when I've gotten you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不事做一半  钱也拿一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't take half pay for a job half done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个很有趣的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an interesting proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们缺的就是一个统一的主题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we're missing is a unified theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能协调全国广告投入  组织跨党派活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we coordinate on national ad-buys, organize crossover events,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,开发捐款应用  应该能收效颇丰...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}develop fund-raising apps, I think it would go a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧  但我觉得总统不太可能同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe, but I doubt the leadership will go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你能支持  我安排了一次会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I'd like your support. I set up a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是能来  并且支持我的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you came, and you supported my position...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计他们最终会说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just think they're gonna end up saying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不能为全国范围的策略烧钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can't be thinning out our funds on a national strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要落到实处  争取选票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about fieldwork, getting out the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  但至少该考虑一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, but isn't it worth at least some consideration?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解我的  琳达  我喜欢大胆的点子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know me, Linda, I mean, I'm all for bold ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  飞机是我们那位中国朋友的公司的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但博奇和乌麦克  他们太守旧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Birch and Womack, why, they're... set in their ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  来过多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们不太可能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt very seriously that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  2005年起来堪萨斯城38次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  弗兰克  我只想要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, Frank, all I'm asking is that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们唱反调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you play devil's advocate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  给我点时间  我有点要紧事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, excuse me for a moment. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这事我很在乎的  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to short-shrift this, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  我要你去问他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  先让我发完这条短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I know, but I just have to send this text.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是闲人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am busy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  当着面他不好撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  已经买票了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国航空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-请给我订靠过道的座位    -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Make sure that's an aisle seat.   - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉着你根本不重视这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't feel as if you're taking this very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,琳达  我向你道歉  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linda, I apologize. I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得没错  我没有敷衍你的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are absolutely right, I did not mean to sound curt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的  这是很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are right, this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,咱俩这就好好谈谈你的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I should go through your proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细推敲每一个细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and discuss it right down to the last detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想让你逐字逐句地看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not asking you to go through it page by page,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要帮忙让他们愿意认真考虑就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just to help me initiate some meaningful dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-我当然会帮你了  琳达    -多谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can count on my help, Linda.   - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-我会让排程员联系你这边    -好的  琳达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I will have my scheduler reach out to yours.   - Thank you, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请接内线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me a secure line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统来电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,通常我会无视你的来电  但我今天心情不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Normally, I would ignore your call, but I am in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没法破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even you could ruin it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是在向共和党捐款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you funneling money to the Republicans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给了共和党超级政治行动委员会大概两千万\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About 20 million in GOP Super PACs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我从不给政党捐款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you know I never make political contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易让我的投资者不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the fastest way to upset my investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道钱的来路 是密苏里的一家赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the money is coming from a casino in Missouri
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我还知道是冯给的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I know it's from Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,冯先生和我只合作过一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng and I have one co-venture together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而且和赌博毫无关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it has nothing to do with gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他的一架私人飞机定期飞往拉尼根的赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A plane that he owns flies to Lanagin's casino on a regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他私人时间做什么  与我无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What he does on his own time is no business of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想给领导层添乱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you trying to create chaos in the ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,共和党没有我的帮助似乎也做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Republicans appear to be doing a fine job of that without my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会得逞的  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not gonna work, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这只会让民主党更团结  而不是分裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll bind the democrats together, not pull us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要我猜的话  过去十年里让民主党团结的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What has bound them together the past decade has been
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是资助你们成为多数党的捐助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the means to achieve a majority, if I had to guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是他用钱铸就了国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He stacked Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,铸就了我任党鞭的多数党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The majority I whipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原来一直是你在操纵  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's been you, Raymond, all along,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根的钱流向我们的时候也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even when Lanagin's money was coming to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你总在做我已经否认的假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep making assumptions that I have denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等季度报告一出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once the quarterly filings come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有电脑的人都会明白是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anybody with a laptop is gonna see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在九月底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The end of September.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还早着呢  但我很期待看到那些报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a long way off. But I look forward to seeing the reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在中期选举两周前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should make for some very interesting reading
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是很有趣的读物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two weeks before the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你别想靠恐吓回到决策桌上  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot bully your way back to the table, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你也休想收买国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just as you cannot buy the keys to Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你成功维持众议院多数席位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Best of luck keeping your majority in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那对你来说意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how much it means to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱给你用的时候  大家都不会多想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the money's coming your way, you don't ask any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但这下清楚了  拉尼根不过是个幌子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now it's clear. Lanagin's never been anything but a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉总统吗  不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I tell the president? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他会想我之前怎么不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll wonder why I didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就显得消息不灵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which makes me look uninformed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他会责备传话的人  把他也卷进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or he'll blame the messenger for involving him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就显得我太大意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which makes me look careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是个陷阱  我得守住这个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's a trap. I must keep this to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他问你代表谁进行购买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants to know who you are buying on behalf of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一家名叫水星资本的对冲基金  还没上市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a hedge fund named Mercury Capital. It's unlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要主要投资者的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need the names of the principal investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我得保护他们的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him I have to protect identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,代理人需要更多信息  他要完整的投资人名单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The broker needs more. He wants a full investor list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就说主要投资者和白宫联系密切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say that the principal investor has strong ties to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们问你是不是代表克雷顿-维斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they want to know if you represent Clayton West.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,克雷顿-维斯特吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clayton West?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}搜索  克雷顿-维斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷蒙德·斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-他还在等    -稍候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's waiting.   - One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}搜索  冯山德  雷蒙德·塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写了些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于一家中国的稀土精炼厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about a refinery in China for rare earth elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说是  告诉他主要投资者是雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him yes. Tell him the principal investor is Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是道格·斯坦普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Doug Stamper...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们该用什么招待沃克夫妇    -氰化物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What should we serve the Walkers?   - Cyanide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,用来做甜点好了  主餐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saving that for dessert. What about a main course?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种肉  或是蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meat of some sort? Vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在不太擅长这方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, this isn't really my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想  不如找弗莱迪来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking, what about Freddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-吃肋排吗    -这样会不会太唐突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ribs?   - Or is that gauche?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  我喜欢这主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I like the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用高档瓷器  精致配菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we can do the nice china, gourmet sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得肋排更有人情味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think the ribs make it more personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我去打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你正在等的这通电话有消息吗    -还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Any word on the call you're expecting?   - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他的航班应该还没到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think he's landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真搭起来了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is really coming along, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得小孩子气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think it's childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,总比打游戏好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's better than video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的五千美金支票带来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have my check for $5,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等我涨工资了再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time when I get a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌场运气不好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad luck at the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克知道我在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So Tusk knows I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-丹尼尔·拉尼根知道    -塔斯克跟这事有关吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Daniel Lanagin knows you're here.   - Is Tusk involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would I admit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克和你有生意来往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk is in business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你在给拉尼根汇钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sending money to Lanagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根的赌场又归塔斯克管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lanagin's casino is in Tusk's backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你大老远飞来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't fly halfway around the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不会就是为了证实猜测吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}world just to confirm suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.28,0:24:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想中止资金继续流向共和党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want the money to stop flowing to the Republicans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what do I receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.17,0:24:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了我们想要的  现在到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've told you what we want. Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好让你再次误导我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, so you can mislead me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,形势变了  误导你对我们没有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things have changed. We have nothing to gain by misleading you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我的花园如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think of my garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.32,0:24:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只知道谈生意  就会忘记欣赏美景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you only talk business, you stop appreciating beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么时间赏景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have much time for beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你们这些老板有闲暇赏景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For people like you to smell the flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.25,0:24:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这些手下得去除杂草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some of us have to pull the weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.13,0:24:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-打算什么时候走    -还没买回程票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When do you plan on leaving?   - I haven't bought my return ticket yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.71,0:24:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要考虑一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to think on this for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.90,0:24:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你一定累坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm sure you must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.59,0:24:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可否赏脸在这儿做客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you do me the honor of being my guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常感谢    -很好  你能休息一下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'd be very grateful.   - Excellent. You can get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.44,0:25:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有很多美的事物可以享受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are many beautiful things to enjoy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.69,0:25:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.70,0:25:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  见面了  冯山德在拖延
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.45,0:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  没得到答复绝不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  对了  我们圣路易斯和堪萨斯的朋友知道我在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.07,0:25:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  带那位印第安朋友来华盛顿  我要当面会会他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}道·斯坦普  这就和堪萨斯联系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.87,0:25:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.89,0:25:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  格雷森先生到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, Mr. Grayson is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.30,0:25:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.07,0:25:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你上任以来我们还一直没机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I haven't really properly had the chance to sit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好好坐下聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and have a chat since you came on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要我改进的吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything I can be doing better, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  你很厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No. I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.28,0:26:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你很聪明  也有很好的职业素养\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're very smart. Excellent work ethic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.97,0:26:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但更重要的是  你的洞察力很强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But more importantly, you're very observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.58,0:26:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,信息就是力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Information is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在这间屋子里  我妻子向世人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was right here in this room that my wife revealed a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.56,0:26:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,吐露了惊人的消息  成千上万的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of information to a great number of people. Millions of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  如果你是担心我所知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, if your concern is my knowledge of any discrepancies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.65,0:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then let me assure you --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.41,0:26:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔和我都很注重隐私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire and I are very private people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.24,0:26:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你为何会不信任我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can understand why you might mistrust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.71,0:26:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有敏锐的洞察力  就像你  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm also observant, like you, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是会有盲点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I still have my blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.89,0:26:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会想到去找马博利太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would have never occurred to me to reach out to Mrs. Marbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.12,0:26:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她丈夫去世了  也没留记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her husband was dead. He kept no records.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还是找到了  白纸黑字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet there it was, in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.74,0:26:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你把它交给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I respect the fact that you brought it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我们为什么会录用你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what got you in the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.99,0:26:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但想要留下  这还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you want to stay, I need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.82,0:27:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是什么居心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What exactly are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我受雇于雷米·丹顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hired by Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.75,0:27:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我来找你们的把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants anything damaging that I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.68,0:27:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-他有日记的备份吗    -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Does he have a copy of the journal?   - No copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.75,0:27:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我把原件交给了安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave the original to Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.30,0:27:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他  她的话属实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I told him that her story checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.69,0:27:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还给了他什么    -我手上没别的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did you give him anything else?   - I don't have anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就算有我也不会给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't give it to him if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.65,0:27:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你现在才说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why am I only hearing about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是美利坚合众国的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you're the vice president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米在为雷蒙德·塔斯克卖命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy works for Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.65,0:27:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我夹在了两位极有权势的人之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That puts me between two extremely powerful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.76,0:27:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,得小心为好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.99,0:27:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米肯定答应给你一大笔钱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure that Remy's offering you a great deal of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但他只能给钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's all he offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.05,0:27:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你在参议院推动福利改革法案时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I saw you push entitlement reform through the Senate,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.67,0:27:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻就明白了谁才是白宫最有权力的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was clear to me where the real power in the White House is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.44,0:27:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为你这样的人效力  不是乘游艇兜风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to work for a man like you, not sail a yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.91,0:27:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,钱我不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Money doesn't interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.17,0:28:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我中止和雷米的接触吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to cease contact with Remy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.54,0:28:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我想让你找到盲点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I want you to find the blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.77,0:28:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-他有空吗    -只有几分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is he free?   - For a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.19,0:28:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢    -墨西哥城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you.   - Mexico City,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.95,0:28:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在那里见到苏托总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where you'll meet president Soto.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.13,0:28:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在飞机上练习西班牙语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can practice your Spanish on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.27,0:28:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么    -弗兰克送我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is that?   - Frank gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.14,0:28:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有时间吗    -有要紧事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you have a minute?   - Yeah, is it important?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.63,0:28:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见...什么时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a meeting with... When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.01,0:28:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经在等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's already in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.34,0:28:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约大主教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The archbishop of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.68,0:28:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想问今天晚餐要不要带礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just wondering if we should bring a gift to dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是家常便饭  可以带瓶酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, it's casual. Maybe a bottle of wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.30,0:28:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他们很熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.39,0:28:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,知道他们喜欢什么酒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea what sort of wine they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.11,0:28:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也不算太熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not extremely well,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.95,0:28:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我可以问问他们的手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm friendly with their staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.63,0:28:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-我会去问明白的    -我可以打电话问问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll figure it out.   - I can make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.83,0:28:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和我丈夫说话  不过谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm having a conversation with my husband, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.33,0:28:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的  对不起    -我在官邸等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- OK. I apologize.   - I'll see you at the residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.21,0:28:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,七点半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven-thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.54,0:29:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.84,0:29:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.85,0:29:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不  请离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just... Please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.90,0:29:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,请出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋  是我  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, it's me. I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.00,0:30:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该接我的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you should answer when I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.54,0:30:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like leaving messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.41,0:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.51,0:30:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉  我只有15分钟吃饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ayla, I get 15 minutes to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.44,0:30:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这还算不忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.16,0:30:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冯山德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.41,0:31:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.42,0:31:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳跟我提过和中国的非正式沟通渠道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor told me about a back channel with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有推测认为是一个叫冯山德的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was speculation it was a guy named Xander Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.57,0:31:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,14分52秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}14 minutes, 52 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.29,0:31:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他和雷蒙德·塔斯克有生意往来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in business with Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.65,0:31:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在中国一起经营一家精炼厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're working on a refinery in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.34,0:31:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克与白宫有关联\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk has ties to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,14分37\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}14 minutes, 37 --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,美国最有钱的富翁之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the wealthiest men in America
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.21,0:31:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个中国幕后外交官做生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in business with an off-the-books chinese diplomat?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而他对华盛顿的影响力从未见报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Influence in Washington never been reported?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.67,0:31:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫在能源危机的紧要关头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House pushes rare earth subsidies
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.43,0:31:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,推动核能补贴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the energy crisis spiked?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要问什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a specific question for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请教副总统对此的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to ask the vice president about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.70,0:31:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么具体要问我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A specific question for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.79,0:31:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是要求安排采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not an interview request.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.95,0:31:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统认识雷蒙德·塔斯克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does the vice president know Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.91,0:31:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,据我了解不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒什么  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're hiding something, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.91,0:31:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有隐瞒任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.61,0:31:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是饿得血糖有点低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just a guy with low blood sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.51,0:31:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.08,0:31:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.80,0:31:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她总来烦我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.08,0:31:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像她过分地想要帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like she's trying too hard to be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让琳达和她谈谈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have Linda talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.65,0:31:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不止是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.18,0:32:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这只是表象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like it's a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.18,0:32:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还有别的隐情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like there's something else going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.40,0:32:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.60,0:32:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我走进办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes, when I walk into your office
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.40,0:32:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看见她在和你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and see her talking to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩总一起出差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and you've been traveling together so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.76,0:32:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  特莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.99,0:32:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说你  但她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, not you, her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.66,0:32:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为她喜欢上你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she's attracted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.18,0:32:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她以前也...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she does have a history--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.43,0:32:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我们居然在讨论这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't even believe we're having this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你把她调走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to relocate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.61,0:32:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,让她去别的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find her another position--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.72,0:32:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.84,0:32:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这似乎有点反应过度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it seems overboard--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.80,0:32:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个很好的助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a good aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对琳达很有帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's valuable to Linda,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.31,0:32:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她也是政府的人才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which makes her valuable to the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.88,0:32:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.61,0:32:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该比这些更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should be more valuable than either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.31,0:32:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-特莉莎    -她明明让我不舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tricia.   - I don't understand why you're fighting me on this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.60,0:32:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么还跟我争    -我们马上就到弗兰克家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- when she bothers me   - we're pulling up to Frank's in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.39,0:32:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太美味了  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really, superb, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.61,0:32:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can honestly say
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.72,0:32:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从没吃过这么好的肋排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have never had better ribs in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.96,0:32:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴您喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm glad you liked you them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.48,0:32:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在《太阳报》上看到报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I read the article in the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.43,0:33:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,写你去弗莱迪的餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about how you go to Freddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意我接受采访  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you don't mind me speaking to that reporter, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.83,0:33:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了  我忘了我不该这么叫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh shit, I forgot I'm not supposed to call you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.51,0:33:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你想  我也不会让你叫我"副总统"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't let you call me "Vice President" even if you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.50,0:33:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我完全不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I didn't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.56,0:33:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那篇报道非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought the article was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.85,0:33:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,报道出来以后生意一下兴隆了不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's been a big bump in business since it came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.24,0:33:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,街上排起大队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm talking lines around the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你不是唯一去那里的白人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not the only white person to show up there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.94,0:33:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了  明天还要早起呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm gonna call it a night. I got a early start in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.83,0:33:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们  总统先生  沃克夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a pleasure meeting you, Mr. President. Mrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A pleasure. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.21,0:33:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,随时为你效劳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.36,0:33:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不用了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. None -- none for me, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.84,0:33:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  一块派有益心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, a slice of pie is good for the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-我吃饱了    -吃一块派没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm stuffed.   - You can have a slice of pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.05,0:33:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不用了  谢谢你  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine, really, but thank you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.43,0:33:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.94,0:33:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩也要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the two of us, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.89,0:33:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她又要逼我多跑五英里把它消化掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now she is gonna make me run another five miles to work off this puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.91,0:33:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗  我几乎跟不上你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you crazy? I can barely keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.40,0:33:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你比我快多了    -你们一起跑步吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're so much faster than me.   - You two run together?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.28,0:34:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  时间很难找  但我们还是挤出时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It's hard to find the time, but somehow we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  而且只有我和他在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do. And it's something that's just ours, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.54,0:34:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  只有咱俩  再加八个特情局特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Just ours. And about eight Secret Service agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.53,0:34:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩能一起跑步真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's so nice that you have that together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.05,0:34:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望加勒特和我能有更多时间做那样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish Garrett and I had more time for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.15,0:34:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾一起去上过动感单车课\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did take a spinning class together once.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.13,0:34:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真该看看加勒特在手把上弯着腰的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have seen Garrett hunched over the handlebar --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.83,0:34:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.83,0:34:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再来点酒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like some more wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.28,0:34:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢  我看到你送他的沙袋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would, thank you. I saw the punching bag you gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧  我来一块派吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? I will have a slice of pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.88,0:34:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请给总统上一块派\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pie, please. For the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.68,0:34:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.54,0:34:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我从头到尾读了一遍  我觉得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I read it front to back. I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.66,0:34:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}2014军队反性侵法案
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.94,0:34:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会掀翻天  但也许这正是我们需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll cause a shit-storm, but maybe that's what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.98,0:34:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在中期选举间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not during the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.69,0:34:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不出有招致批评的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't see how we take flack.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.18,0:34:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是想减少强奸啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're trying to curtail rape, for godsakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.56,0:34:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  一些右翼人士会老调重弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, some right-wingers will do their usual song and dance--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.25,0:34:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,先别急  我想自己看过再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold off. I want to read it myself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向副总统承诺我们会找联署人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We promised the Vice President we'd have cosponsors...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们承诺了什么  我们要拖延\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what we promised, and we're gonna stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要把草案泄露出去    -但你知道法案的要点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't disseminate the draft.   - But you know the gist of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.01,0:35:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不明白为什么不能    -洛莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't see why we can't--   - Lorrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.58,0:35:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那你先看着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I'll leave it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.34,0:35:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-还有别的事吗    -不  没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Anything else?   - No. I think we're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.09,0:35:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Then I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.51,0:35:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,跟老公的约会之夜  还不如杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Date night with the husband. Slit my wrists, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.09,0:35:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了就回家  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go home at some point, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.97,0:35:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,国会大厦明天早上还会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Capitol will still be here in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.42,0:35:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷米·丹顿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.54,0:36:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这可真棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.78,0:36:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完工呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ways to go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.33,0:36:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谁赢了这场战役  北方还是南方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, who won this battle? The North or the South?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.85,0:36:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,双方都伤亡惨重  没有明显的赢家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Massive casualties on both sides. No clear winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.13,0:36:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会有时间干这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you find the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.70,0:36:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我零零散散挤出半小时  能让我放松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I carve out a half hour here and there. Helps me relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.02,0:36:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我都忘了什么叫放松了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've forgotten the meaning of that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.75,0:36:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,送你沙袋就是干这个用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's what the punching bag is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.32,0:36:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.25,0:36:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一点就行  特莉莎和我过会儿该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a little. Tricia and I should get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样的话一个任期都挺不过去  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're never gonna make it through this first term, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.48,0:36:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,此话怎讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.19,0:36:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可不行  让压力渐渐累积\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not like this. Letting the stress creep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.19,0:36:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要跑马拉松  而不是冲刺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to run the marathon, not the sprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.59,0:36:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该学会享受忙里偷闲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to enjoy these little moments of escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.75,0:37:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,多倒一点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can pour more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.00,0:37:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.68,0:37:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是联军还是叛军    -联军  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This Union or rebel?   - Union, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.20,0:37:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别再叫"先生""总统先生"  叫名字吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough "Sirs" and "Mr. Presidents." Call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.76,0:37:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我尊重你的职位  不能那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I respect the office too much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.68,0:37:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,私下里没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we're in private, it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.25,0:37:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚  我不必扮演总统的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight, I don't have to be president.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.28,0:37:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是有意要介入你们的私生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't mean to get involved in your personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.75,0:37:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是我提起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. I brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.36,0:37:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是为了克里斯蒂娜吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this really about Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是别的什么事的表征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe it's just a symptom of something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.07,0:37:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-比如呢    -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Like what?   - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.17,0:37:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎见不到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I barely see him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.73,0:37:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在很紧张  海外局势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's so wound up in everything that's going on overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.78,0:37:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,中期选举  经济危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the elections, the economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.19,0:37:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他当州长的时候  也不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he was governor, it wasn't a cake walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.33,0:38:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但跟现在是不能比了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it was nothing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.44,0:38:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你和弗兰克是怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you and Frank do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.64,0:38:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看起来那么亲密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You both seem so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.78,0:38:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对彼此很坦诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're honest with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.01,0:38:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么都不会藏着掖着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't sweep anything under the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎  如果这事让你很困扰  和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia, if it's eating at you, make him talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.01,0:38:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫不过是一时的  婚姻是一辈子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House is finite. Your marriage is for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.37,0:38:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-早上好    -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good morning.   - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.67,0:38:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢这道汤吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't like your soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我用不好筷子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not good with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得与昨晚的女伴相比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you'll like this soup more than you liked the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.00,0:38:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这道汤会更合你口味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two companions I sent you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.88,0:38:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我太累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.82,0:38:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑过我们昨天说的事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you had a chance to think about what we discussed yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.54,0:39:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国  接到礼物推辞一次是礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In China, it's polite to refuse a gift the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.77,0:39:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我该拒绝你的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I should refuse yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.54,0:39:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不知道你想要什么  我们没法送你礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't offer you a gift if I don't know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,杰斐逊港大桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Port Jefferson Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.63,0:39:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在私下沟通时把项目撤下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You pulled it, during the back-channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.11,0:39:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-我改主意了    -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I changed my mind.   - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.56,0:39:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我有盟友想修建这座桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have allies who want the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没了桥  他们就会变成敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without it, they become my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-我已经两次受审    -腐败指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've been put on trial twice.   - Corruption charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.73,0:39:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国  我这个层次的人都会贿赂该贿赂的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone in China who works on this level pays who they need to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.84,0:39:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,杀掉该杀的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they kill who they need to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.65,0:39:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,总有人莫名消失  斯坦普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People disappear all the time, Mr. Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.22,0:39:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可能消失  你也可能消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could disappear. You could disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.07,0:39:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别再去赌场  我们就给你这座桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop the junkets, and we'll get you the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.64,0:39:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,先把桥定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bridge comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.20,0:39:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统骗过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president has lied to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.64,0:39:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看到他诚意的证明  才会停止资金流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need proof of his commitment. Then the money will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.15,0:39:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,斯坦普先生  请用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, Mr. Stamper. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.38,0:40:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你接下来要坐很久的航班呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a long flight ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.58,0:40:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得你一定要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it's what you feel you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.85,0:40:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人  我在这儿工作很愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've had a great experience here, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.91,0:40:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个机会我实在没法错过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is an opportunity I can't pass up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我猜钱肯定给得不少    -确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I imagine the pay is substantial.   - It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.96,0:40:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但不只是钱的事  在太空探索技术公司有上升空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's not just that. There's room to grow at SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.13,0:40:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你决定了  我不会劝你留下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if your mind's made up, I won't try and convince you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.69,0:40:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话  我最初来的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is... when I first came on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.94,0:40:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为是同时为你和你丈夫工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought it was to work for both you and your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.12,0:40:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别误会  为你工作我十分荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get me wrong, it's been an honor working for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.95,0:40:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没想到要和赛斯一起工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I didn't foresee having to work with Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.81,0:40:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-你俩有些不合    -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're not very fond of each other.   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.54,0:40:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是问题  我们都是专业人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is fine. We're professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.18,0:40:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这样最好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.38,0:40:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,雇佣出色人才的问题就在于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the problem with hiring great people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.35,0:40:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都想把他们撬走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is everyone wants to steal them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.75,0:40:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很感激你能这么善解人意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate you being so understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.20,0:40:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们会想念你的  康纳    -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You'll be missed, Connor.      - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.21,0:41:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯  是我  他刚离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, it's me. He just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.51,0:41:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和他谈谈  然后发一篇新闻稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talk to him and put out a press release.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.95,0:41:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尽可能地平稳过渡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's make this as smooth as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.51,0:41:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我感兴趣的有两个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's two opportunities I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.67,0:41:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗莱迪烧烤餐馆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.07,0:41:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,家族连锁餐厅  和零售烧烤酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Family-oriented restaurant chain and a retail barbecue sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.93,0:41:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,具体是什么内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would that look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.19,0:41:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你一笔预付款来购买你的品牌使用权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We give you an upfront payment for the right to use your brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.61,0:41:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管这两项投资是否失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either venture fails, or they both do,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.61,0:41:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那些钱都还是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you still get to keep that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.69,0:41:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是多少钱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much money we talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.43,0:41:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你签合同  9万5千\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}95,000 as soon as you sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.90,0:41:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果买卖成功了  你还会有收益分红\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you'd have a share of the profits if we're successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,分红怎么分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would the shares be?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.71,0:41:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧  我草拟一份合同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll tell you what. Let me draw up papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.98,0:41:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好看一遍  然后给你的律师看一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look them over. You show them to your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那你得找一个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you should get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.94,0:41:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你觉得自己被骗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want you to feel like you're being cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.59,0:41:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有疑虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're skeptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.36,0:41:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.69,0:42:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是想买排骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}money usually don't come through that door
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.65,0:42:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一般没人送钱上门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless it's looking for a plate of ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.77,0:42:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想卖成千上百的肋排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we want to sell thousands of those plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.28,0:42:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果加盟店建立起来  将数以百万计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Millions, if the franchise builds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,《太阳报》的文章让你名声大噪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Sun article put you on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.15,0:42:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们用弗莱迪烧烤连锁店撑起这个名声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's fill up that map with Freddy's barbecue joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.51,0:42:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在看什么    -你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What are you looking at?      - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.84,0:42:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,刀在厨房里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The knives are in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.49,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你有枪  不用一直盯着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a pistol. You can stop staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.63,0:42:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了吗  丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is he in here? Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.04,0:42:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好吗    -挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How are you?   - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.62,0:42:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝一杯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Care for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.55,0:42:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去客厅吧  那里更舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's, uh, go into the living room. It's more cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.85,0:42:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, I'm just fine where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.33,0:42:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也行  你先下去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, all right. Uh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.53,0:42:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.70,0:42:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定告诉雷蒙德我请你来这儿了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you've told Raymond that I've asked you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.75,0:42:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond who?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.46,0:42:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在我面前你不用装  丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you don't have to pretend, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.56,0:42:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,冯证实了你的企图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng confirmed what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.25,0:43:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听过这人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Name doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.51,0:43:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有航班记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have flight records.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.58,0:43:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他的一架飞机多次飞往堪萨斯城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of his planes to Kansas City on multiple occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要继续玩下去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do we really have to play this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.48,0:43:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是因为我以为你有什么好提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came here because I thought you might have something to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.97,0:43:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不如直接切入正题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't we just skip to that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.82,0:43:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直是个忠诚的捐助人  丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been a loyal contributor, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.30,0:43:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你为我们募集资金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've thrown us fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.64,0:43:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多我们握手的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are pictures of you and I shaking hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.91,0:43:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以无论你这一季度做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So whatever you've done this quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.43,0:43:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以一笔勾销\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.61,0:43:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的资金得停止流往错误的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I need the money to stop flowing in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.57,0:43:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在等你的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still waiting for the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.09,0:43:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个商人  丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a businessman, Dan,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.21,0:43:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道利益是你的首要考虑    -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- so I know your primary concern is profits.   - Well, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.19,0:43:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在要给你比金钱更有价值的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm offering you something that's far more valuable than money:
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.58,0:43:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,直通白宫的关系线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a direct line to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.27,0:43:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去太含糊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds vague to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.81,0:43:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我对印第安人事务局有影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have influence over the BIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.91,0:43:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,关于联邦赌博立法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over federal gambling legislation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.73,0:43:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经靠捐款买到了这种影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sort of influence that my contributions have already bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.15,0:43:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没有直接参与  你在总统那边也说不上话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with my direct involvement and the president's ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.25,0:43:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我最喜欢钱哪一点吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what I like about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.88,0:44:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我能把钱摞在桌子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can stack it on a table, like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.30,0:44:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我能用尺子去丈量它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can measure it with a yardstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.99,0:44:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见它  闻到它的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see it, smell it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.17,0:44:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,用它买任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}buy things with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.65,0:44:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,房子  车子  衣服  实实在在的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Houses, cars, clothes. Things that are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.88,0:44:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让我看到更多诚意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna have to show up with more than beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.88,0:44:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,丹  我请你来我家是因为我认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dan, I invited you to my home because I thought --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.75,0:44:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从后门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.21,0:44:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.39,0:44:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我从后门进来  像佣人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Through the back door, like a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.04,0:44:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,特勤局要求所有人都从后门进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Secret Service makes everyone come in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.11,0:44:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是防范措...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a precautionary meas--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你给我的钱能多过塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you're gonna offer me more money than Tusk --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.59,0:44:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而我认为你做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't think that you can --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.41,0:44:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我们就没什么商量余地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's little left for us to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在向你提供机会和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am offering you an alliance with a man
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.91,0:44:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在宾夕法尼亚大街1600号工作的人结盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who goes to work every day at 1600 Pennsylvania Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不信任何白人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't place my faith in any white man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.53,0:44:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是为联邦政府做事的白人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially one that works for the federal government.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.50,0:44:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一样  丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am just like you, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.58,0:44:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道白手起家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what it means to start from nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.04,0:44:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,杀出一条路的艰辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to have to fight your way --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.34,0:45:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道我走到今天的艰辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know nothing about what it means to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.27,0:45:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你所谓的白手起家  比我起步的时候要阔绰得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your version of nothing was light years ahead of where I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.23,0:45:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我尊重你  丹  我重视你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I respect you, Dan. I take you serious--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等我在乎你的尊重时  我会告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know when I give a fuck about your respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.51,0:45:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,郝利戴  送拉尼根出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Holiday? Show Lanagin out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.14,0:45:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道后门在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know where the back door is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.53,0:45:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.00,0:45:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没摔坏  我能修好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not broken. I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.88,0:45:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别管它了  我一会儿收拾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave it. I'll clean up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.71,0:45:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去跑步  让你消消火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go for a run. Burn off some of this steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.09,0:46:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.00,0:46:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be out in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.96,0:46:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走  你赶上我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll go ahead. You catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.94,0:46:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你上飞机前为什么没联系我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you reach out, before you got on a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.33,0:46:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心我们的通讯被监视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was afraid our communication might be monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和拉尼根进展如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we with Lanagin?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.20,0:46:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有进展  你和冯呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nowhere. Where are we with Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.12,0:46:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许有个选择  但会比较棘手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We might have an option, but it's gonna be tricky.
